    "",
    "SOURCES",
    "State legislative seats: NCSL State Partisan Composition (ncsl.org)",
    "Congressional seats: Wikipedia List of Current US Representatives (Feb 2, 2026)",
    "Mississippi updated to reflect Nov 2025 special election results.",
    "",
    "HOW TO UPDATE",
    "Edit this file in GitHub whenever seats change hands.",
    "Update the _updated field for the state you changed.",
    "Commit with a message like: Update TX composition - special election Jun 2026",
    "",
    "FIELDS",
    "CD = Congressional Districts (US House seats)",
    "SS = State Senate",
    "SH = State House / Assembly",
    "d = Democratic seats, r = Republican seats, i = Independent or other seats",
    "total = total seats in chamber",
    "",
    "SPECIAL CASES",
    "Nebraska has a unicameral nonpartisan legislature.",
    "  SS contains all 49 seats. SH is null.",
